         <div type="letter" xml:id="d4e38">
            <pb n="1" facs="0012_000435_000205_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e39"/>
            <p>Philadelphia Jan. 27/56</p>
            <p>Hon A J Donelson</p>
            <p>New York</p>
            <p>My Dear Father</p>
            <p>I wrote to you yesterday at the Metropolitan For fear that my letter did not reach you, I send this on by <unclear reason="illegible" resp="EMS">Alderman Dodge</unclear> of New York, who was introduced to me here by Mr. Westcott. Please write to me immediately when you will be here, or whether I had better come to New York to see you. I must see you before you start south. All well when I left home. Ma had not yet left her bed. I congratulate</p>
            <pb n="2" facs="0012_000435_000205_0002.jpg" xml:id="d4e54"/>
            <p>you again on your nomination.</p>
            <p>Your affectionate son</p>
            <p>AJ Donelson</p>
         </div>
      </body>
